abstract: Trump 2020 may sound a lot like Trump 2016, but this time around the fusion of president and party is complete.
snippet: Trump 2020 may sound a lot like Trump 2016, but this time around the fusion of president and party is complete.
lead_paragraph: Donald Trump has been the most persistently unpopular first-term president in the postwar era. Much of the nation is exhausted and embarrassed by his presidency, pining for normalcy, eager to change the channel. The president’s own internal polls show Mr. Trump trailing the former vice president, Joe Biden, not only in many battleground states Mr. Trump won in 2016, but in traditional Republican strongholds like Georgia.

abstract: To blaze trails, they travel a familiar path.
snippet: To blaze trails, they travel a familiar path.
lead_paragraph: Pete and Chasten Buttigieg celebrated their first wedding anniversary on Sunday. You know this if you’re among Pete’s roughly 1.1 million Twitter followers or Chasten’s 340,000, because they traded sweetly effusive missives, as they frequently do.

headline_main: Pete and Chasten Buttigieg Are a Traditional Wonder

abstract: The shooting of a black resident by a white police officer has revived scrutiny of Mr. Buttigieg’s sometimes strained relationships with the black community.
snippet: The shooting of a black resident by a white police officer has revived scrutiny of Mr. Buttigieg’s sometimes strained relationships with the black community.
lead_paragraph: SOUTH BEND, Ind. — Mayor Pete Buttigieg remained in South Bend, Ind., on Tuesday to confront a local crisis involving the fatal shooting of a black resident by a white police officer, skipping scheduled campaign appearances in Hollywood.

headline_main: Buttigieg Facing Test of Leadership After Shooting in South Bend

abstract: Mr. Buttigieg pulled himself off the presidential campaign trail this week after a police officer in South Bend shot and killed a black man. Here’s some context.
snippet: Mr. Buttigieg pulled himself off the presidential campaign trail this week after a police officer in South Bend shot and killed a black man. Here’s some context.
lead_paragraph: In a crowded Democratic presidential primary field, Pete Buttigieg, the 37-year-old mayor of a midsize Midwestern city, has enjoyed a meteoric rise from obscurity that has become the envy of his lesser known rivals.
